title: New findings in lobster sex change research (University of the Sunshine Coast)
text: ( Source : University of the Sunshine Coast ) A PhD student from the University of the Sunshine Coast is filling vital gaps in knowledge about the sexual development of an Australian lobster species at risk of over-harvesting. Jennie Chandler
